f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得好過有啲另一半wfc你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得嚇親係種care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n你話佢嚇完即刻搵方法幫你就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說ching可以講多啲其他moment～"},{"pid":"ab6107aec0700a14114b6d519da9832ed85b1eb3","tid":926541,"uid":75232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"知道自己無乜自制力，搵到個可以治到我，督促到我嘅仲唔娶返嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c9ee8fbb68cee8853ff3de26150ab9ea233eb2","tid":926541,"uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"簽唔簽都冇所謂啦，我只係想同佢永遠一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb9d263ecfb83a7442077e8e4bfe76245b44539","tid":926541,"uid":182475,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T18:53:53.000Z","msg":"結婚唔止係搵愛人，愛情(特別係激情)只係一部份。<br />\n結婚其實係搵個有愛情成份嘅人同你經成生活/ 人生嘅「隊友」。因為「為對方著想」、「尊重對方細節上不同」、「人生有共同大方向大目標」、「有交帶」，呢啲全部都係在「不失自我及他人」嘅情況下有「團隊精神」嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\n而真正嘅愛，在於你選擇一個當初同你三九唔識七又無血緣關係嘅人，同佢組成呢個 team。情況就好似兩個人面對世界呢個大戰場，你地搵到對對方有愛情有(過)激情有好感嘅人，然後大家都交條命俾對方去組隊。成件事係 band of brothers/ sisters 嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家果啲好感動嘅位，其實係大家果下發現互相有決心或意願成為呢種「隊友」。而反過來離婚啲積怨，或有時見到啲人好自私/ 自我中心/ 懶/ 老奉，其實就係最撚無團隊精神，一心諗住在個隊入面 free-ride 對方嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 咁而家識揀好老公好老婆啦？千萬唔好搵著果啲無團隊精神嘅自私精呀..."},{"pid":"ab088602bf18ecb78e7e442eec09c59d84404eec","tid":926541,"uid":222196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62b2b230826c7ddcc5e6caae03995b295554e47","tid":926541,"uid":220778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"婚姻外既人想跳入婚姻，婚姻內既人想跳出婚姻。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係咪有睇過《圍城》"},{"pid":"543fb228ca1bd010c3d4f41a49b7603e4a84b682","tid":926541,"uid":124330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc5bb862a5a0e85ecc97dcaa57b3026913942967","tid":926541,"uid":46263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f339cd50e9165dc145d4fc3dc3381b6c9e12322d","tid":926541,"uid":124330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1c2c07ed102dde5ddb302897c660c15f8f776ba5","tid":926541,"uid":46263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:58:50.000Z","msg":"真心覺得 決定結婚既人好勁 感覺自己依世都無依種勇氣<br />\n加油呀你 決定咗就要堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同你另一半一齊努力努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"當你遇到一個排除萬難都想同佢一齊既人<br />\n份勇氣就會出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"但要雙方都想同有心先得<br />\n有時都會遇到話想同你走下去既人<br />\n但自己心底裏都係相信唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:11:08.000Z","msg":"信心問題只有自己先幫到自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪有咩不快經歷"},{"pid":"aa2dac91ecb6bf3b40c150a8861b308631a23dbf","tid":926541,"uid":161462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4a17eda93422bbc5b040285f30b9fc34c889daa","tid":926541,"uid":46263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"唔計未婚懷孕個啲<br />\n咩原因 會令你做到依個一生人既決定<br />\n想聽下各方面既睇法 <br />\n歡迎已婚人士講下自己既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:30:23.000Z","msg":"想自己一世都插同一個美麗西<br />\n對方食同一枝大肉腸"},{"pid":"f5e533897fe4f469f9a5c8b805ae9d7ad4699527","tid":926541,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:37:25.000Z","msg":"愛"},{"pid":"b121b3ca70c1d7bb819fb37f20d5961